definitions.definition: A person from Swaziland / Eswatini or of Swazi/Swati descent originally migrating from Central Africa.

main_definition: A person from Swaziland / Eswatini or of Swazi/Swati descent originally migrating from Central Africa.

definitions.definition: A Bantu language primarily spoken in Swaziland/Eswatini and the South African regions adjacent to it.

main_definition: A Bantu language primarily spoken in Swaziland/Eswatini and the South African regions adjacent to it.
